study_pop.textblock:
        1. Initial stage of uveitis: The first episode of uveitis without treatment;

          2. Remission of uveitis: Uveitis caused by various reasons in the stable disease period
             of more than 3 months without treatment;

          3. Relapse of uveitis: After discontinuation of uveitis treatment, the disease stabilized
             for more than 3 months.
